EN: Where can I buy cheap clothes?

ZH: 你打算跟谁去哪儿？
EN: Who are you planning to go with?

ZH: 我应该放哪儿呢？
EN: Where should I put it?

ZH: 你说的那篇文章在哪儿？
EN: Where is the article you were talking about?

ZH: 这个城市的最好的景点在哪儿？
EN: Where are the best tourist attractions in this city?

